  "texts": [
    "P form, we selected the models with accuracy and cross-validation R 2 scores above arbitrarily chosen threshold values based on preliminary evaluations of a thousand random forest regression models for each target variable.",
    "The threshold values chosen (Table 3) were defined to enable our model selection to result in a minimal number of models after training the pool of models for each target variable.",
    "The selection criteria, the number of selected models for each target variable, the mean accuracy (Aµ), and cross-validation R 2 of the selected models are presented in Table 3.",
    "The model accuracy is defined as accuracy = 100 -MAPE (%).",
    "We calculated two additional model evaluation metrics; the mean absolute error and the coefficient of determination (not to be confused with the cross-validation R 2) for each selected model for all P forms."
  ]
